### ============================================================
### 日志管理接口
### ============================================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken =

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 日志列表 (支持分页和筛选)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 默认分页
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 带分页参数
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 按状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20&status=success
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 按模型筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20&model=dashscope_qwen3_coder
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 按时间范围筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&limit=20&from=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-05-25T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 获取单条日志详情 (替换 {logId} 为实际 ID)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/{{logId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 重放请求 (替换 {logId} 为实际 ID)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/{{logId}}/replay
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 重放请求 — 指定模式 (mode: exact / historical)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/{{logId}}/replay?mode=exact
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 重放请求 — 自定义请求体
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/{{logId}}/replay
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "dashscope_qwen3_coder",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 清理过期日志 (根据 retention_days 设置)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 导出日志 (JSON 格式)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/export
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 导出日志 — 筛选 + JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/export?status=success&model=dashscope_qwen3_coder
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 导出日志 — CSV 格式
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 导出日志 — 按时间范围 + CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs/export?format=csv&from=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-05-25T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 导出统计数据
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 默认 24 小时
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/export
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 近 7 天
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/export?range=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 近 30 天
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/export?range=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
